c=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWSVdxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWSVdxw.jpg&h=3a775622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16e65fa57f58da4a2fafc67637f221227e73fcb4","tid":1745292,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:10:24.000Z","msg":"和理非唔知點抗爭？唔想放棄？<br />\n 入黎進修啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［進擊的和理非］<br />\n和理非武裝化 - 知識篇 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/eyJDKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/eyJDKT</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"60f4825204aebd2af3261c4ef00843b765694d01","tid":1745292,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e5a8b1207375679685bc7066081494809858a4f5","tid":1745292,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82312cffe075308388083d90e36b9aedf8a216e9","tid":1745292,"uid":41116,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"點解寫明已用過嘅彈殼唔計都入到？<br />\n有無法律撚解答<br />\n點解佢就罰錢 個記者就還押唔比保釋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:02:46.000Z","msg":"邊度寫明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:10:53.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;彈藥&rdquo; (ammunition)指 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)供&ldquo;槍械&rdquo;定義(a)、(b)、(c)、(d)及(g)段範圍內的槍械使用的彈藥；<br />\n(b)容載或經設計或改裝以容載任何&ldquo;槍械&rdquo;定義(e)段範圍內的有害液體、氣體、粉末或其他類似東西的彈藥；<br />\n(c)榴彈、炸彈或其他相類的投射物(不論是否可與槍械配合使用)，以及此等物體的信管、雷管及引爆管；<br />\n(d)根據《工廠及工業經營條例》(第59章)所訂有關槍彈推動打釘工具規例所界定的&ldquo;槍彈&rdquo;；<br />\n(e)行政長官會同行政會議為施行本條例而在根據第52條所訂規例中宣布為彈藥的任何東西；  (由1999年第13號第3條修訂)<br />\n(ea)射彈、子彈或投射物，或構成(a)、(b)、(c)、(d)或(e)段所指的彈藥的某件物品的並非屬射彈、子彈或投射物的部分；  (由2000年第14號第2條增補)<br />\n(f)任何炮彈殼或槍彈殼，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>但不包括 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)只能作滅火用的手榴彈；<br />\n(ii)只用作私人、住戶或辦公室裝飾用品的射彈、子彈或投射物、已使用的或空的炮彈殼或槍彈殼，或只作此用的構成(a)、(b)、(c)、(d)或(e)段所指的彈藥的某件物品的並非屬射彈、子彈或投射物的部分；  (由2000年第14號第2條代替)</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9620d8075c10996bfaf17063c14d033390763cc8","tid":1745292,"uid":1049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7f013c3305c29fe0d07c4afc206dabf4bcb3e1d4","tid":1745292,"uid":312332,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"82312cffe075308388083d90e36b9aedf8a216e9","tid":1745292,"uid":41116,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"點解寫明已用過嘅彈殼唔計都入到？<br />\n有無法律撚解答<br />\n點解佢就罰錢 個記者就還押唔比保釋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"因為用過既彈殼可以重新refill彈藥，變成新既子彈<br />\n<br />\n其實條例本身目的係怕真子彈殼重新refill<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過有機會係槍膛爆炸/軌道不穩定</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"不過法例真係寫左不包括已使用的或空的炮彈殼或槍彈殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17a4a27c2f95a7e0065dc6bdf3c031947e1a92f","tid":1745292,"uid":206224,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191122/s00001/b0d653b0f1dcc59ddb101309c0bd2135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191122%2Fs00001%2Fb0d653b0f1dcc59ddb101309c0bd2135.jpg&h=2513efe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄籍被告Startsev Aleksandr（余卓祈攝）"},{"pid":"93a4ae451561212af411ee822ab3c90d6aa4d0ee","tid":1745292,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f013c3305c29fe0d07c4afc206dabf4bcb3e1d4","tid":1745292,"uid":312332,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"82312cffe075308388083d90e36b9aedf8a216e9","tid":1745292,"uid":41116,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"點解寫明已用過嘅彈殼唔計都入到？<br />\n有無法律撚解答<br />\n點解佢就罰錢 個記者就還押唔比保釋"},"citedB